Hello, thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, your go-to bowling alley. My name is Jamie. May I ask who I'm speaking with today?

Hi Jamie, my name is Alex.

Nice to meet you, Alex! How can I assist you with your billing inquiry today?

Sure, I recently received a bill and there seems to be an error. I was charged one zero zero dollars for a single session.

I’m sorry to hear about the confusion, Alex. Let me help you with that. Could you please confirm the date of the session in question?

Of course. It was on October fourteenth.

Thank you. For verification purposes, may I have the last four digits of your contact number?

Sure, it's three four five six.

I appreciate your patience, Alex. I've checked your billing records and see the charge should have been fifty dollars, not one hundred dollars. I'll correct this for you right away.

Great, thank you so much for your help, Jamie.

You're welcome, Alex. Thank you for your understanding and for bringing this to our attention. Have a great day!
